    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/98b87167d15cb9ee1d952cc3d007f45b.poster.avif?t=1771760712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/98b87167d15cb9ee1d952cc3d007f45b.webm?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/98b87167d15cb9ee1d952cc3d007f45b.mp4?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>HOVERDRIVE </strong>is a 3D platformer where you drive a gravity-defying hover car! <br>Reach <i>The Core</i> at the end to complete each level, but beware of <i>The Core</i>'s defenses...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jump, Boost, Drift, HOVERDRIVE</h2>The hover car is highly agile with its ability to <i>Jump </i>and then <i>Boost </i>mid-air!<br><br>Use <i>Boost</i> to get around quickly which refills by performing sick tricks like Roll, Flip, Spin, Drift, and Air-Time! <br>Tricks are scored as a style grade, no pressure...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect the Things</h2>Skillful and curious players are rewarded with collectable <i>Datapaks</i>.<br>Also, collect dozens of <i>Bits</i> scattered throughout every level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/d5938a65db0f7767549fdb3e2879ad93.poster.avif?t=1771760712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/d5938a65db0f7767549fdb3e2879ad93.webm?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/d5938a65db0f7767549fdb3e2879ad93.mp4?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roadmap to Beta</h2>The game is currently in the alpha stage of development, with the following ongoing changes being made towards a beta:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Finalize art assets<br></li><li>Controller support<br></li><li>Unique mechanics for special levels<br></li><li>A <i>lot</i> more levels<br></li><li>More polish and juice!</li></ul>Be sure to follow the Steam page for development updates!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/e1cca2fb2acb6bea7e7835f116b6c3ff.poster.avif?t=1771760712\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/e1cca2fb2acb6bea7e7835f116b6c3ff.webm?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074590/extras/e1cca2fb2acb6bea7e7835f116b6c3ff.mp4?t=1771760712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
